Package: zanthror
Type: Package
Title: Stata `zanthro` Extension Ported to R - Anthropometric Analysis Tools
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Warren Holroyd
Maintainer: Warren Holroyd <warrenholroyd@gmail.com>
Description: Classifies BMI values using International Obesity Task Force (IOTF) 
    age and sex-specific cutoffs. Replicates the functionality of Stata's 
    zanthro extension with vectorized performance and labelling options.
URL: https://github.com/w4rhol/zanthror
BugReports: https://github.com/w4rhol/zanthror/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Imports:
    stats,
    labelled,
    haven,
    sitar
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5.0)
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
